    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.48
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = 0.15
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.04 * tmp + 0.87)) + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.36) + 0.94))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.66)
    tmp = 0.59
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.57 * v1 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
